snippet.textDisplay: medi save sounds good. plus governments artificially lowering costs. you are forced to save a percenmtage of your salary and probably have to pay a percentage of the medical cost. while the government picks up the rest.  you can possibly choose to higher your rate if needed or pull out money from the savings if its not being used after a while. this seems like a balanced system.
